post_summaries.description: The Instagram post by @gaynorfitnessandtravel shows a video of clear turquoise water with a sandy beach and some boats in the background. The caption mentions a snorkeling trip to Catalina Island, a BBQ, swimming, and seeing the homes of famous people like Pitbull and Shakira, as well as the river where Jurassic Park and Wakanda were filmed.
The image shows a collection of buckets and containers filled with freshly caught fish in Santa Maria, Sal, Cape Verde.
The image shows a woman, presumably Gaynor from gaynorfitnessandtravel, preparing to zipline in Cabo Verde. She's wearing a harness and standing on a platform overlooking the ocean.
A woman is walking on a sandy beach with turquoise water in Cape Verde. The caption says "Life's a beach" and includes hashtags related to travel and gratitude.

The Instagram post shows a picture of a blizzard encountered during a snowmobile trip in Finnish Lapland, while searching for the Northern Lights. The post also mentions seeing the Aurora Borealis from the hotel and on the flight home.
The image shows a person (presumably gaynorfitnessandtravel) feeding reindeer at a reindeer farm in Lapland. The person is wearing winter clothing and the scene is snowy.
